Here's the English version of the README file:

````markdown
# Adidas Style Landing Page

A responsive Adidas product showcase landing page featuring running shoes.

## ✨ Key Features

- Modern minimalist design
- Responsive layout (supports 950px-1150px screens)
- Dynamic gradient background effect
- Interactive navigation menu
- Product image display section
- Smooth hover animations

## 🚀 Quick Start

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Abdelrhman612/Adidas_Style.git
```
````

2. Open `app.html` directly in your browser

## 🎨 Project Structure

```
adidas-style/
├── app.html          # Main page
├── style.css         # Stylesheet
└── images/           # Image assets
    └── shoes.png     # Main product image
```

## 🔧 Tech Stack

![HTML5](https://img.shields.io/badge/-HTML5-E34F26?style=flat&logo=html5&logoColor=white)
![CSS3](https://img.shields.io/badge/-CSS3-1572B6?style=flat&logo=css3)

- Pure HTML5/CSS3 implementation
- Flexbox layout
- CSS animations
- Media queries for responsiveness
- Glassmorphism effect

