## 🔄 Customization

Modify these CSS variables for customization:

```css
:root {
  --main-red: #e80202; /* Primary red color */
  --background-gradient: linear-gradient(#111, #222); /* Background gradient */
  --glass-effect: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); /* Glass effect transparency */
}
```

